curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/3650' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8273-1/SGM8273-2/SGM8273-4", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8273-1 (single), SGM8273-2 (dual) and  SGM8273-4 (quad) are low noise, high precision, high  voltage operational amplifiers, which can operate from  3.3V to 36V single supply or from ±1.65V to ±18V dual  power supplies. They provide rail-to-rail input with a  wide input common mode voltage range and rail-to-rail  output voltage swing.  The SGM8273-1/2/4 provide high slew rate, low noise,  low offset, drift and bias current.  The SGM8273-1 is available in Green SOT-23-5,  SOIC-8 and MSOP-8 packages. The SGM8273-2 is  available in a Green SOIC-8 package. The quad  SGM8273-4 is available in a Green SOIC-14 package.  They are specified over the extended -40℃ to +125℃  temperature range.    "}'
